│                                                                              │
│ **Moving Through the Pipeline**                                              │
│ Once payment clears, the order moves to "confirmed" status. This triggers    │
│ our inventory system to reserve the items. The warehouse team then picks up  │
│ the order, moving it to "processing" as they gather and pack the items.      │
│                                                                              │
│ **Shipping & Tracking**                                                      │
│ When the package leaves our facility, we mark it as "shipped" and attach     │
│ tracking information. This allows both us and the customer to monitor the    │
│ package's journey. The carrier updates us as the package moves through their │
│ network.                                                                     │
│                                                                              │
│ **Final Delivery**                                                           │
│ Once the carrier confirms delivery, we update the status to "delivered". The │
│ customer receives notification, and the order lifecycle is complete.         │
│                                                                              │
│ **Exception Handling**                                                       │
│ Sometimes things don't go as planned. Customers might cancel before          │
